clause_text: The narrator was performing their usual job tasks in a warehouse
The narrator had been working for several hours
The narrator was working on the warehouse floor
attributing it to hunger from not eating
The narrator experienced a strange tightness and pressure in their chest while working
and resting against a wall did not alleviate the symptoms
The narrator was working in a warehouse
The narrator had symptoms of heart pounding
The narrator was working in a warehouse
The manager noticed the narrator's distress
and attempted to check on them
The narrator was working in a warehouse
and felt lightheaded due to hunger
The narrator began to see spots
The manager noticed the narrator's distress
and caught them as they were about to collapse
The narrator began to see spots
and was unable to breathe properly
The manager noticed the narrator's distress
and assisted them before they collapsed
The manager noticed the narrator's distress

The warehouse manager noticed the narrator's distress
